column1: Houses Sold by Type of Financing
1Includes houses reporting other types of financing. Beginning in 2008, also includes Rural Housing Service.
S   Withheld because estimate did not meet publication standards on the basis of response rate,
associated standard error, or a consistency review.
Z  Less than 500 units or less than 0.5 percent.
Note: Estimates prior to 1999 include an upward adjustment of 3.3 percent made to account for
houses sold in permit-issuing areas that will never have a permit authorization.
